{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/change-the-position-of-overlapping-elements-with-the-z-index-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Promenite poziciju preklapajućih elemenata koristeći z-index svojstvo","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada su elementi postavljeni na preklapajući način (tj. koristeći <code>position: absolute | relative | fixed | sticky</code>), element koji se pojavi kasnije u HTML oznakama će po defaultu biti iznad drugih elemenata. Međutim, <code>z-index</code> svojstvo može specificirati redosled kako se elementi slažu jedan iznad drugog. Mora biti ceo broj (tj. broj bez decimalnog dela), i veće vrednosti <code>z-index</code> svojstva elementa uzimaju višu poziciju u redosledu od onih sa manjim vrednostima.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a3367417b2b2512acf","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Dodajte <code>z-index</code> svojstvo elementu sa klasom <code>first</code> (crveni pravougaonik) i postavite ga na 2 kako bi bio iznad drugog elementa (plavi pravougaonik).</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cM94aHk","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301046,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/change-the-position-of-overlapping-elements-with-the-z-index-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  div {\n    width: 60%;\n    height: 200px;\n    margin-top: 20px;\n  }\n\n  .first {\n    background-color: red;\n    position: absolute;\n\n  }\n  .second {\n    background-color: blue;\n    position: absolute;\n    left: 40px;\n    top: 50px;\n    z-index: 1;\n  }\n</sty